Computer Vision Engineer Roadmap\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Computer Vision Engineering focuses on enabling machines to understand, interpret, and analyze images and videos. A Computer Vision Engineer works on tasks like object detection, image classification, face recognition, segmentation, and video analysis using deep learning and classical vision techniques.\
This roadmap takes you from programming basics to building advanced real-world vision systems used in industries like healthcare, autonomous driving, robotics, and security.\
